/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同cityhall d 人報串篤佢間野出黎<br />\n等佢個地址畀cityhall blacklist <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08b0e95f2223ac3ef10d22f9c83d947ac8e91f59","tid":106652,"uid":6136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T23:11:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>hostelworld 冇名既好打極有限</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我同事熱烈推介airbnb咪試下囉<br />\n邊有諗犯唔犯法架<br />\n我琴晚係maastricht個小鎮都係住airbnb<br />\n不過佢就唔係hostel形式 係自己多間房<br />\n其實我見我book果間hoatel附近都好多hostel既物體 六合彩又唔見我中</blockquote><br />\nBook果陣有冇其他人評語<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"332c0d364182b7c983a4073a7745686cec416d1c","tid":106652,"uid":13652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T23:13:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>hostelworld 冇名既好打極有限</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我同事熱烈推介airbnb咪試下囉<br />\n邊有諗犯唔犯法架<br />\n我琴晚係maastricht個小鎮都係住airbnb<br />\n不過佢就唔係hostel形式 係自己多間房<br />\n其實我見我book果間hoatel附近都好多hostel既物體 六合彩又唔見我中</blockquote><br />\nBook果陣有冇其他人評語<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多人讚 好多人住過 我住果晚都full<br />\n我做咩都會做好多research先<br />\n今次真係千年道行一朝喪"},{"pid":"6721e559797c07e7f9f143bba40576c49b08223c","tid":106652,"uid":13652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T23:14:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>哇你係Amsterdam 嘅經驗都好差下<br />\n咁都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依d奇遇真係一百歲唔死都有故仔聽<br />\n聽日d人黎調查我都覺得有d古怪<br />\n問佢地係咪illegal又話唔係<br />\ndklm 明知我會擺d野係到都唔單聲<br />\n由我死即日封 陷家鏟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同cityhall d 人報串篤佢間野出黎<br />\n等佢個地址畀cityhall blacklist <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果日我地答佢地d問題已經等於篤左啦<br />\n佢應該永久收皮架喇"},{"pid":"ac313984fb6fb23adfff27a