moji\" />"},{"pid":"0f244fcb495c8a475cf6ecc38d4437198733e73a","tid":106652,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T23:29:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依d奇遇真係一百歲唔死都有故仔聽<br />\n聽日d人黎調查我都覺得有d古怪<br />\n問佢地係咪illegal又話唔係<br />\ndklm 明知我會擺d野係到都唔單聲<br />\n由我死即日封 陷家鏟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同cityhall d 人報串篤佢間野出黎<br />\n等佢個地址畀cityhall blacklist <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果日我地答佢地d問題已經等於篤左啦<br />\n佢應該永久收皮架喇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫佢收皮<br />\n<br />\n樓主星期一做到野嘅機會大d<br />\n但佢地咁慢手腳⋯<br />\n不如諗下可唔可以extend 張機票搞呢件事<br />\n人在當地就最方便搞呢d野<br />\n盡快要決定啦<br />\n有d airline 係24小時前先改到<br />\n你果間要自己問問"},{"pid":"36df4a36504edb9529285f310485e9b29c74a5d3","tid":106652,"uid":13652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T23:29:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>瞓街體驗當地街頭文化。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已經搵到新hostel 沖埋涼 攤左係床喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b13002155a654598be9065c1eda08c9fca8023","tid":106652,"uid":13652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T23:29:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前幾日先去完荷蘭 都係住hostel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主黑仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你住邊間呀 參考下 我黎緊兩晚仲未book<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"968562cc24d08c307b889db08ef1294221da98f2","tid":106652,"uid":13652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T23:30:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有啲錢唔鏗得...</blockquote><br />\n慳啊巴打</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真絲 冇諗住慳架 真係貪個廚房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb96ed5e704647af7496092055d4e65eca1aee05","tid":106652,"uid":13652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s